module.exports = {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeffry.in","author":"Jeff Wainwright"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"/Users/jwainwright/Dropbox/me/git-docs/yowainwright.github.io/src/pages/2017-03-03-arrow-functions-cont.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p>Note post: this short post continued from my 1st <a href=\"https://jeffry.in/arrow-functions/\">Arrow Functions Post</a> after trying out some more things with Arrow Functions with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/dansbenson/\">Dan Benson</a>.</p>\n<p>Arrow Functions can be even simplier (sometimes)! 💪 In the example below, the parans <code>()</code> around arguments are not needed so there ommitted as are the mustaches <code>{}</code> around the returned function.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&apos;button&apos;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nbutton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&apos;click&apos;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">&apos;here&apos;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Here’s a Codepen for <a href=\"http://codepen.io/yowainwright/pen/ac6ec21ee8bc9a4ec8dbdfbe56778626\">fun</a> purposes.</p>","frontmatter":{"featured_image":null,"meta":"This post reviews some things about arrow functions that I learned from Wes Bos's ES6 for everyone.","title":"Arrow Function Notes After Watching ES6 For Everyone, Continued","date":"March 03, 2017","path":"/arrow-functions-cont/"}}},"pathContext":{"path":"/arrow-functions-cont/","_PARENT":"SOURCE"}}


